# UNPROLOGUE Corporate Website

Corporate website for UNPROLOGUE株式会社, inspired by [mederi.jp/company/](https://www.mederi.jp/company/).

## Quick Start

Serve locally with any static file server:

```bash
python3 -m http.server 8080
```

Then open http://localhost:8080

## Structure

- `index.html` — Company overview page
- `css/styles.css` — Styles
- `js/main.js` — Scroll animations, mobile menu, interactions
